  "body": "this is off latest HEAD as of now `4e2641319be2fd33a8cd61f0258456b7cef07957`\r\n\r\nso was syncing and then sent signal to stop `CTRL-C`\r\n\r\nand at downloader.go:617, a routine calls `.Cancel()`\r\nbut at download.go:569, another routine also calls `.Cancel()`, \r\n\r\nthis causes a race condition on downloader.go:597 aka, two routines writing to `d.ancientLimit = 0`\r\n\r\nnot sure how important this is though - but it is wrong ",
